{"tid":2389441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2021 諾貝爾和平獎提名  環保少女 v 川普","createTime":"2021-02-01T02:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T02:25:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e6b4ca8c6cb3f0182d1be6d658df22c8ee3a7d7b","tid":2389441,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T02:06:07.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯反對派領袖納瓦尼、世界衛生組織及瑞典環保少女童貝里都獲得今年諾貝爾和平獎提名，他們都是由挪威國會議員提名。2014年以來和平獎得主幾乎全都來自挪威議員提名。<br />\n<br />\n據路透社報導，美國前總統川普和白俄羅斯反對派領袖季哈諾夫斯卡婭（Sviatlana Tsikhanouskaya）也在提名名單中。<br />\n<br />\n從世界各地國會議員到諾貝爾得獎者等成千上萬的人，都有資格提名候選人。提名將在今天結束，獲提名不意味就會獲得諾貝爾委員會認可。<br />\n<br />\n奧斯陸和平研究中心（PRIO）主席烏達爾（Henrik Urdal）表示，自2014年以來，諾貝爾和平獎得主都出自挪威國會議員提名人選，僅2019年除外。<br />\n<br />\n根據路透社對挪威國會議員的調查，被提名者包括環保少女童貝里（Greta Thunberg）、俄羅斯反對派領袖納瓦尼（Alexei Navalny）、世界衛生組織（WHO）及其2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）疫苗全球取得機制（COVAX）。這項機制要確保貧窮國家公平獲得疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n童貝里因身為「對抗氣候危機最重要代言人」之一獲得提名，她和他人共同創立的「週五為未來而戰」運動（Fridays for Future）也獲得提名。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦尼除獲得俄羅斯學者提名，也「因為俄羅斯和平民主化所做的努力」而獲挪威前部長埃爾維斯圖恩（Ola Elvestuen）提名。<br />\n<br />\n對抗疫情是目前全球關切核心，因此除了世衛組織，全球疫苗與預防注射聯盟（GAVI）也獲得提名。<br />\n<br />\n資訊自由是反覆出現的主題，被提名者包括總部設在美國的保護記者委員會（Committee to Protect Journalists）、前「查理週刊」（Charlie Hebdo）記者拉祖伊（Zineb el-Rhazoui、香港自由新聞（Hong Kong Free Press）網站、總部設在美國的國際事實查核聯盟（International Fact-Checking Network, IFCN）和總部設在巴黎的無國界記者組織（Reporters without Borders, RSF）。<br />\n<br />\n2021年諾貝爾和平獎得主將在10月揭曉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=891082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D891082&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=7679135d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D891082&h=03acaf54\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=891082</a>"},{"pid":"2bff13e670f1c3125ce21701ca40111fe2fb39d2","tid":2389441,"uid":152476,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T02:11:24.000Z","msg":"WHO都提名得<br />\n不如提名香港人同台灣，最早察覺武肺係大獲野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f1455b975557e0b0cfc23047034b58bd302faf","tid":2389441,"uid":127575,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T02:12:36.000Z","msg":"成個諾貝爾都比人收買咗啦"},{"pid":"81e1ff7053328a2e8589620ffe769594a9c0f6bc","tid":2389441,"uid":55941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T02:13:52.000Z","msg":"how dare you 1賠1.00000000001"},{"pid":"fb832ce33e3871269464861b5691c693459e4a87","tid":2389441,"uid":8308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T02:14:33.000Z","msg":"CHO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全世界死幾百萬人就係佢唔做野"},{"pid":"8b05034670c8e6236e4da66d0558eb309c800ed2","tid":2389441,"uid":87780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T02:18:18.000Z","msg":"諾貝爾關公獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b2f0fbe7b3275d5f2a6418e393bf507de39c2a","tid":2389441,"uid":64073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T02:19:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86dff272268ff3d2c6cbdccf8817cc56a00210d","tid":2389441,"uid":133806,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T02:19:42.000Z","msg":"我提名武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\n一個肺炎令到工廠唔開，飛機飛少咗，全球污染物一下子減少<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uHARY2C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuHARY2C.jpg&h=b53c3494&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e2961544fc9bd88dd058266e5ebc7b208cab77d","tid":2389441,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T02:21:12.000Z","msg":"